                                positioned at 45 degrees, creating gentle shadows that add structure to the face. The
                                background is a smooth, neutral grey seamless paper with no visual distractions. The
                                composition frames the subject from the upper chest to just above the head, with sharp
                                focus locked on the eyes and a subtle depth-of-field blur on the shoulders. The result
                                is a clean, trustworthy, and authoritative LinkedIn profile picture that commands
                                professional respect and builds instant credibility with recruiters and colleagues.
