                                expression is confident yet warm, with a natural slight smile and direct eye contact
                                that communicates competence and approachability. The composition is clean and
                                well-centered, optimized for LinkedIn's circular profile picture crop with the face
                                positioned in the upper third. Soft diffused lighting creates an even, shadow-free
