                                large nearby window creates a soft, organic glow with gentle shadows that add dimension
                                without being distracting. The framing is simple and balanced, with the subject centered
                                and photographed from the shoulders up. The image has a calm, understated quality with
                                natural color tones and no heavy editing  conveying professionalism through simplicity
                                and letting the person's genuine presence shine through.
